title: Mueller’s 49 Questions, The Good Yellow Fever 5.1.18
itunes:title: Mueller’s 49 Questions, The Good Yellow Fever 5.1.18
description:
In episode 138, Jack and Miles are joined by comedian Biniam Bizuneh to discuss Michelle Wolf's response to the WHCD criticism, May Day rallies, Puerto Rico continuing to protest because the US has failed them, Mueller's questions for Trump being leaked, midterm elections coming up, Whole Foods partnering with the restaurant Yellow Fever, Kraft's new Oreo style for China, & more!
